  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      50.19,
      165.75,
      293.83,
      191.3
    ],
    "text": "BE it enacted by the Parliament of the Democratic Socialist Repubiic of Sri Lanka as follows :-",
    "fonts": [
      "*Minion Pro-9182"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.5
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      49.89,
      202.08,
      290.71,
      227.71
    ],
    "text": "1.This Act may be cited as the Code of IntellectualProperty (Amendment) Act, No. 40 or 2000.",
    "fonts": [
      "*Minion Pro-9182"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.5
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      49.44,
      238.53,
      293.07,
      300.47
    ],
    "text": "2.Section 6 of the Code of Intellectual Property Act,No. 52 of 1979 (hereinafter referred to as the \"principal enactment\") is hereby amended by the insertion immediately after the definition of \"broadcasting\" of the following new definitions :-",
    "fonts": [
      "*Minion Pro-9182"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.5
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      62.14,
      311.35,
      292.83,
      337.17
    ],
    "text": "' \"Computer\" means an electronic or other device having the capability of storing and processing information ;",
    "fonts": [
      "*Minion Pro-9182"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.5
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      60.95,
      348.09,
      292.31,
      422.38
    ],
    "text": "\"Computer programme\" means a set of instructions expressed in words, codes, schemes or in any other form, which is capable, when incorporated in a medium that a computer can read, of causing the computer to perform or achieve a particular task or resut. \u2022.",
    "fonts": [
      "*Minion Pro-9182"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.5
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      47.98,
      433.28,
      291.81,
      483.36
    ],
    "text": "3.Section 7 of the principal enactment is hereby amendedin subsection (2) of that section by the repeal of paragraph (j)of th'at subsection and the substitution of the following paragraphs therefor :-",
    "fonts": [
      "*Minion Pro-9182",
      "*Times New Roman-Italic-9177"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      9.0,
      10.5
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      64.53,
      493.91,
      292.07,
      531.6
    ],
    "text": "\"(j) illustrations, maps, plans, sketches and three dimensional works relative to geography, topography, architecture or science ;",
    "fonts": [
      "*Minion Pro-9182",
      "*Times New Roman-Italic-9177"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      9.0,
      10.5
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      66.92,
      542.96,
      181.66,
      557.4
    ],
